(firstQuint)Could a Simple Information Booklet Modify Low Back Pain Patients Beliefs After Lumbar Discectomy?.

 A translation / back-translation of the Your back operation was performed and a before / after prospective study was realized.

 Main outcome assessment was the Quebec Questionnaire.

 Demographic data, personal medical sciatica pain history, graduation of the whole subject were recorded.

 Acceptability of the booklet was also measured.

